{"word":"G2544 - καίτοιγε - kaítoige - kah'-ee-toyg-eh - Nevertheless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καίτοιγε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kaítoige</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kah'-ee-toyg-eh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Nevertheless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"இருந்தும் - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"nevertheless, though"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2543 - καίτοι - kaítoi - kah'-ee-toy/2543\">G2543</a> and <a href=\"#/G1065 - γέ - gé - gheh/1065\">G1065</a>; <i>and yet indeed</i>, that is, <i>although really:</i> - nevertheless, though.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}